# Copy this file to .env and fill in values.
# Never commit .env to git.
#
# NOTE: Most site configuration lives in src/data/site-config.json
# (church name, schedule, ticker text, YouTube channel/playlist IDs, etc.)
# No environment variables are required for the app to run.
#
# Only add variables here if you need to override config at build time
# without touching source files (e.g. in CI/CD pipelines).

# Example (not currently used by the app):
# VITE_SITE_URL=https://filadelfia.live
